snippet.title: POWDER Roguelike Pixel RPG
snippet.description:
Pixelish roguelike that is open source and free.
✅ More #OpenSourceGames http://bit.ly/OSGames 🔴 Subscribe now!
💎 Join our chat at https://discord.gg/usAHQdz !
💬 Write a comment about your favorite moment!
POWDER is from http://www.zincland.com/powder/index.php?pagename=about
How to Win
Descend into the depths of the dungeon until you reach the foul daemon known as "He who the author cannot spell consistently", or, Baezl'bub. When you have slain Baezl'bub in heroic combat, or, if Baezl'bub dies in any way, retrieve his black heart and bring it to the surface world.
